\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:simple publication bias"

\end_inset

 Assume 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 independent samples from the simple publication bias model 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:selection for significance model"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 Then, for any 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

, any confidence set for 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{0},\tau$
\end_inset

, or 
\begin_inset Formula $(\theta_{0},\tau)$
\end_inset

 with level 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha>0$
\end_inset

 will have infinite diameter with positive probability.
 
\end_layout

