\begin_layout Remark
The mixture probability 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi^{k}$
\end_inset

 is positive if and only if 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{k}\neq0$
\end_inset

.
 This allows us to parameterize the general publication bias model using
 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi=(\pi^{1},\pi^{2},\ldots,\pi^{k})$
\end_inset

 instead of 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

